The United States has to stop the Chinese military, but they are no match for Chinas war machines.
 They hire the best scientists they can find to quickly develop an anti-android destroyer. They are deployed in the dark of night to help reclaim territories.

Unfortunately, there isn't much success, so the president decides to drop atom bombs on all of the android factories in China. The explosions are so large, they ignite the atmosphere. The civilian casualties are enormous, but not as enormous as they would have been had the Chinese Communist Party been allowed to continue its world domination.

he American president felt bad about the civilian casualties,but felt that they were necessary to bring justice back to the world.
